WEBVTT

00:00.520 --> 00:01.360
Xuan Kingdom's people

00:02.680 --> 00:03.560
Suffer this calamity

00:04.560 --> 00:05.360
If I avoid battle

00:06.800 --> 00:07.880
Then hearts will turn away

00:09.920 --> 00:10.680
Xie Xuan, receive orders

00:11.880 --> 00:12.480
Your general is here

00:12.840 --> 00:13.720
Muster troops and attack

00:14.400 --> 00:15.600
Cover the people entering the city

00:16.240 --> 00:16.520
Orders received

00:18.160 --> 00:18.760
Your Highness

00:19.560 --> 00:20.520
Follow military orders

00:22.360 --> 00:23.000
Yes

00:27.840 --> 00:30.000
Xie's army charges into the enemy formation

00:30.240 --> 00:32.320
Successfully scatters the Wuzhao's supervision team

00:32.600 --> 00:35.480
But is also tightly engaged by the prepared Wuzhao army

00:35.720 --> 00:36.880
That was waiting

00:37.680 --> 00:39.400
Shilang takes advantage to launch a strong attack

00:39.680 --> 00:41.160
You personally lead troops in a desperate defense

00:41.520 --> 00:43.280
Buying time for the people

00:43.280 --> 00:44.720
To escape

00:50.760 --> 00:51.480
A day later

00:52.200 --> 00:53.960
Yiyang falls

00:58.080 --> 00:59.240
You're a real man

01:01.000 --> 01:02.400
I'll give you a quick death
